snippet.title: DiArts
snippet.description:
Hi, my name is Diana Rozevskis (aka DiArts) and my abiding love of mythology, fantasy and reading children's books to my two daughter's inspired me to begin writing 'The Crystal Waters Series' fifteen years ago.
With the seventh, and final book written in the series, I now turn to another passion of mine, Art, and whether it be crafting, painting or digital I feel every step I become a stronger artist (a very similar thing happened as I wrote my book series) and I am so glad of your support and a friend by my side on my magical journey as an artist. 
Thank you so much 💕
